# Secret Variables - Use DevServerControl for security
# Instead of storing passwords in .env, use:
# DevServerControl set_env_variable: ["SERVER_PASS", "your_password_here"]
# 
# Other secrets to set with DevServerControl:
# - STRIPE_PUBLIC_KEY
# - STRIPE_SECRET_KEY  
# - EMAIL_HOST, EMAIL_PORT, EMAIL_USER, EMAIL_PASS
# - ORANGE_MONEY_API_KEY, ORANGE_MONEY_SECRET
# - ADMIN_PHONE, ADMIN_PIN (for production)

